org.antstudio.rbac.domain.annotation
注释类型 MenuMapping

@Target(value=METHOD)
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Documented
public @interface MenuMapping

this annotation is for @RequestMapping method when application start,the url would be generated to menu

版本：
1.0
作者：
Gavin

必需元素摘要
 java.lang.String url
          the url for the menu
 
可选元素摘要
 java.lang.String code
          the menu code,this is for the auto generated menu
 java.lang.String name
          the name for the menu
 java.lang.String parentCode
          the parent menu code,this is for the auto generated menu
